current.title: Happy Dreamsong #5
current.about: I had a really weird dream the night after Thanksgiving at the hotel. I dreamt I was in a "streamer house" with a famous millionaire livestreamer who was ordering his sycophants and his "crew" to make coffee for him. He turned to me and ordered me to do it as well. Instead of doing it I said "what, you think I'm one of those _____s" and one of his main top sycophants heard me and came at me and chased me outside. We were at the top of a mountain with a huge checkerboard staircase going down. He started to violently attack me and I fought back. Someone called the police or something and they came and one of them basically beat the shit out of him. The main thing I remember is after that, a few of us all sat around at the top of the staircase sitting and looked at one another while laughing together -
